    • getTotalElapsedTime

      int getTotalElapsedTime()
      Returns the difference between the time when the top frame was pushed and when it was popped. If the top frame hasn't been popped, or if the stack is empty, returns -1. This is the same as the elapsed time of the entry point frame.
